#. <section class="sutta" id="sn1.50"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn1.50:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 1"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 1"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn1.50:0.2"
msgid "5. Ādittavagga"
msgstr "5. On Fire"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn1.50:0.3"
msgid "50. Ghaṭīkārasutta"
msgstr "50. With Ghaṭikāra"

#. </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.75"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn1.50:1.1"
msgid "“Avihaṃ upapannāse,"
msgstr "“Seven mendicants reborn in Aviha"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:1.2"
msgid "vimuttā satta bhikkhavo;"
msgstr "have been freed."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:1.3"
msgid "Rāgadosaparikkhīṇā,"
msgstr "With the complete ending of greed and hate,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:1.4"
msgid "tiṇṇā loke visattikan”ti."
msgstr "they’ve crossed over clinging to the world.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
#. VAR: paṅkaṃ → saṅgaṃ (bj, s1-3, pts2)
msgctxt "sn1.50:2.1"
msgid "“Ke ca te ataruṃ paṅkaṃ,"
msgstr "“Who are those who’ve crossed the bog,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:2.2"
msgid "maccudheyyaṃ suduttaraṃ;"
msgstr "Death’s domain so hard to pass?"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:2.3"
msgid "Ke hitvā mānusaṃ dehaṃ,"
msgstr "Who, after leaving behind the human body,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:2.4"
msgid "dibbayogaṃ upaccagun”ti."
msgstr "have risen above celestial yokes?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn1.50:3.1"
msgid "“Upako palagaṇḍo ca,"
msgstr "“Upaka and Palagaṇḍa,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:3.2"
msgid "pukkusāti ca te tayo;"
msgstr "and Pukkusāti, these three;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:3.3"
msgid "Bhaddiyo khaṇḍadevo ca,"
msgstr "Bhaddiya and Bhaddadeva,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: bāhuraggi ca siṅgiyo → bahudantī ca piṅgayo (bj) | bahudantī ca siṅgiyo (s1-3, pts2) | bāhuraggi ca piṅgiyo (pts1)
msgctxt "sn1.50:3.4"
msgid "bāhuraggi ca siṅgiyo;"
msgstr "and Bāhudantī and Piṅgiya."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:3.5"
msgid "Te hitvā mānusaṃ dehaṃ,"
msgstr "They, after leaving behind the human body,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:3.6"
msgid "dibbayogaṃ upaccagun”ti."
msgstr "have risen above celestial yokes.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn1.50:4.1"
msgid "“Kusalī bhāsasī tesaṃ,"
msgstr "“You speak well of them,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:4.2"
msgid "mārapāsappahāyinaṃ;"
msgstr "who have let go the snares of Māra."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:4.3"
msgid "Kassa te dhammamaññāya,"
msgstr "Whose teaching did they understand"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:4.4"
msgid "acchiduṃ bhavabandhanan”ti."
msgstr "to cut the bonds of rebirth?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn1.50:5.1"
msgid "“Na aññatra bhagavatā,"
msgstr "“None other than the Blessed One!"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:5.2"
msgid "nāññatra tava sāsanā;"
msgstr "None other than your instruction!"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:5.3"
msgid "Yassa te dhammamaññāya,"
msgstr "It was your teaching that they understood"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:5.4"
msgid "acchiduṃ bhavabandhanaṃ."
msgstr "to cut the bonds of rebirth."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn1.50:6.1"
msgid "Yattha nāmañca rūpañca,"
msgstr "Where name and form"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:6.2"
msgid "asesaṃ uparujjhati;"
msgstr "cease with nothing left over;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:6.3"
msgid "Taṃ te dhammaṃ idhaññāya,"
msgstr "understanding this teaching,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:6.4"
msgid "acchiduṃ bhavabandhanan”ti."
msgstr "they cut the bonds of rebirth.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "sn1.50:7.1"
msgid "“Gambhīraṃ bhāsasī vācaṃ,"
msgstr "“The words you say are deep,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:7.2"
msgid "dubbijānaṃ sudubbudhaṃ;"
msgstr "hard to understand, so very hard to wake up to."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:7.3"
msgid "Kassa tvaṃ dhammamaññāya,"
msgstr "Whose teaching did you understand"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:7.4"
msgid "vācaṃ bhāsasi īdisan”ti."
msgstr "to be able to say such things?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.77"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "sn1.50:8.1"
msgid "“Kumbhakāro pure āsiṃ,"
msgstr "“In the past I was a potter"

#. <br>
#. VAR: vekaḷiṅge → vehaliṅge (bj) | vebhaḷiṅge (s1-3, km) | vehaḷiṅge (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn1.50:8.2"
msgid "vekaḷiṅge ghaṭīkaro;"
msgstr "in Vebhaliṅga called Ghaṭikāra."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:8.3"
msgid "Mātāpettibharo āsiṃ,"
msgstr "I took care of my parents"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:8.4"
msgid "kassapassa upāsako."
msgstr "as a lay follower of Buddha Kassapa."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.36"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "sn1.50:9.1"
msgid "Virato methunā dhammā,"
msgstr "I refrained from sexual intercourse,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:9.2"
msgid "brahmacārī nirāmiso;"
msgstr "I was celibate, spiritual."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:9.3"
msgid "Ahuvā te sagāmeyyo,"
msgstr "We lived in the same village;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:9.4"
msgid "ahuvā te pure sakhā."
msgstr "in the past I was your friend."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "sn1.50:10.1"
msgid "Sohamete pajānāmi,"
msgstr "I am the one who understands"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:10.2"
msgid "vimutte satta bhikkhavo;"
msgstr "that these seven mendicants have been freed."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:10.3"
msgid "Rāgadosaparikkhīṇe,"
msgstr "With the complete ending of greed and hate,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:10.4"
msgid "tiṇṇe loke visattikan”ti."
msgstr "they’ve crossed over clinging to the world.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.78"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "sn1.50:11.1"
msgid "“Evametaṃ tadā āsi,"
msgstr "“That’s exactly how it was,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:11.2"
msgid "yathā bhāsasi bhaggava;"
msgstr "just as you say, Bhaggava."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:11.3"
msgid "Kumbhakāro pure āsi,"
msgstr "In the past you were a potter"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:11.4"
msgid "vekaḷiṅge ghaṭīkaro;"
msgstr "in Vebhaliṅga called Ghaṭikāra."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:11.5"
msgid "Mātāpettibharo āsi,"
msgstr "You took care of your parents"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:11.6"
msgid "kassapassa upāsako."
msgstr "as a lay follower of Buddha Kassapa."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "sn1.50:12.1"
msgid "Virato methunā dhammā,"
msgstr "You refrained from sexual intercourse,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:12.2"
msgid "brahmacārī nirāmiso;"
msgstr "you were celibate, spiritual."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:12.3"
msgid "Ahuvā me sagāmeyyo,"
msgstr "We lived in the same village;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:12.4"
msgid "ahuvā me pure sakhā”ti."
msgstr "in the past you were my friend.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "sn1.50:13.1"
msgid "“Evametaṃ purāṇānaṃ,"
msgstr "“That’s how it was"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:13.2"
msgid "sahāyānaṃ ahu saṅgamo;"
msgstr "when those friends of old met again."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:13.3"
msgid "Ubhinnaṃ bhāvitattānaṃ,"
msgstr "Both of them have developed themselves,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:13.4"
msgid "sarīrantimadhārinan”ti."
msgstr "and bear their final body.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn1.50:13.5"
msgid "Ādittavaggo pañcamo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc14"></a>
msgctxt "sn1.50:14.1"
msgid "Ādittaṃ kiṃdadaṃ annaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:14.2"
msgid "ekamūlaanomiyaṃ;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:14.3"
msgid "Accharāvanaropajetaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.50:14.4"
msgid "maccharena ghaṭīkaroti."
msgstr ""
